OL,3,C'Chaotic and broken': The SEND crisis
OL,4,Cfailing scores of children
OL,6,FA damning report has found children
OL,7,Fwith special educational needs are
OL,8,Fbeing let down by a 'chaotic system',
OL,9,FITV News Social Affairs Correspondent
OL,10,FSarah Corker and Producer Lottie
OL,11,FKilraine report
OL,13,FLike many 10 year olds Bo Elliott-
OL,14,FHoogstraten from Leeds loves animals
OL,15,Fand wants to be a vet when she's older.
OL,17,FArticulate and bright, she has a
OL,18,Fthirst for learning, but unlike her
OL,19,Fpeers she's going without a formal
OL,20,Feducation.
