OL,3,C'Chaotic and broken': The SEND crisis
OL,4,Cfailing scores of children
OL,6,FHer autism and anxiety mean she needs
OL,7,Fextra specialist support in the
OL,8,Fclassroom, which her local primary
OL,9,Fschool couldn't provide.
OL,11,FIt's now been more than two years
OL,12,Fsince she was on the school roll, and
OL,13,Fshe's falling further behind.
OL,15,FHer mother Tesse Elliott Hoogstraten
OL,16,Ftold ITV News: "Bo's already saying
OL,17,Fnow 'mummy I've missed so much of
OL,18,Fschool, I'm scared'.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/16
