OL,3,C'Chaotic and broken': The SEND crisis
OL,4,Cfailing scores of children
OL,6,F"But I say 'don't worry about it'
OL,7,Fbecause at this moment in time, she's
OL,8,Fnot ready for mainstream at all."
OL,10,FFrom the age of five, Bo struggled to
OL,11,Fcope at a mainstream school, suffering
OL,12,Fdaily panic attacks, meltdowns and
OL,13,Flashing out.
OL,15,F"It used to take us two hours to get
OL,16,Fher into school," Her father, Tom
OL,17,FElliot, told ITV News.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/16
