OL,3,C'Chaotic and broken': The SEND crisis
OL,4,Cfailing scores of children
OL,6,F"We were having to pull her from the
OL,7,Ftop of the stairs and manhandle her
OL,8,Finto the car and I just said 'I can't
OL,9,Fdo this to my child anymore.'"
OL,11,FBo's parents have battled for years to
OL,12,Fget her the right support.
OL,14,F"I feel completely let down by the
OL,15,Fsystem and angry because why should we
OL,16,Fhave to suffer so much stress for
OL,17,Fsomething that should be a basic human
OL,18,Fright. Why should we have to fight for
OL,19,Fthat?" Mr Elliott said.
