OL,6,F"The parent's shouldn't be faced with
OL,7,Fthe stress and the financial stress.
OL,8,FIt can break families apart and it can
OL,9,Fhave a massive effect on siblings."
OL,11,FTheir struggles are far from unique.
OL,13,FOn Wednesday the Public Accounts
OL,14,FCommittee (PAC) published a damning
OL,15,Freport that found too many families
OL,16,Fare struggling to access the help
OL,17,Ftheir children with special
OL,18,Feducational needs and disabilities
OL,19,F(Send) "desperately need".
