OL,3,C'Chaotic and broken': The SEND crisis
OL,4,Cfailing scores of children
OL,6,FThe committee said whether children
OL,7,Freceive support depends too much on
OL,8,Ftheir postcode, or how well families
OL,9,Fcan navigate "an often chaotic and
OL,10,Fadversarial system".
OL,12,FIt found demand for Education, Health
OL,13,Fand Care Plans (EHCP), a legal
OL,14,Fdocument setting out additional
OL,15,Fsupport for a child, has soared by
OL,16,F140% in a decade, but said the
OL,17,FDepartment for Education (DfE) does
OL,18,Fnot fully understand why demand for
OL,19,Fsupport has increased, undermining its
OL,20,Fability to deliver it.
