OL,6,FPlans should be issued within 20 weeks
OL,7,Fbut there are huge regional
OL,8,Fdifferences.
OL,10,FFor example, in 2023, local
OL,11,Fauthorities such as Southampton and
OL,12,FBarnet issued 100% of plans within
OL,13,Fthat timeframe.
OL,15,FAt the other end of the scale,
OL,16,FLeicester (0%) the Isle of Wight (0%)
OL,17,Fand Essex (0.9%) failed to deliver any
OL,18,Fplans within the 20 weeks.
