OL,3,C'Chaotic and broken': The SEND crisis
OL,4,Cfailing scores of children
OL,6,FIt's a postcode lottery for families
OL,7,Fwith big differences even between
OL,8,Fneighbouring local authorities. In
OL,9,FYork 96% of plans are written on time,
OL,10,Fwhile in neighbouring Leeds just 8%
OL,11,Fwere.
OL,13,FAlmost half of all councils in England
OL,14,Fin danger of effective bankruptcy
OL,15,Fwithin 15 months - due to persistent
OL,16,Fand significant SEN-related overspends.
