OL,3,C'Chaotic and broken': The SEND crisis
OL,4,Cfailing scores of children
OL,6,FDemand for SEND provision at
OL,7,FMeadowfield Primary School, in West
OL,8,FYorkshire, has nearly doubled in five
OL,9,Fyears - 21% of pupils have a special
OL,10,Feducational need.
OL,12,FIn response, they have set up two SEND
OL,13,Fhubs - space within the existing
OL,14,Fschool - to help provide additional
OL,15,Fsupport for those who need it.
OL,17,FBut funding hasn't kept up with
OL,18,Fdemands and Clare Almond, Assistant
OL,19,FHead and Special Educational Needs
OL,20,FCoordinator, described the system as
OL,21,F"broken".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/16
