OL,3,C'Chaotic and broken': The SEND crisis
OL,4,Cfailing scores of children
OL,6,FClare Almond, Assistant Head and
OL,7,FSpecial Educational Needs Coordinator
OL,8,Fat Meadowfield Primary School,
OL,9,Fdescribed the system as 'broken'
OL,11,FShe says children are arriving in
OL,12,Freception with more complex needs.
OL,14,F"Children have come in with much more
OL,15,Fcomplex needs than previously, and
OL,16,Fit's so difficult to support those
OL,17,Fchildren because a mainstream setting
OL,18,Fis not necessarily the right setting
OL,19,Ffor them," Ms Almond told ITV News.
