OL,3,C'Chaotic and broken': The SEND crisis
OL,4,Cfailing scores of children
OL,6,F"We just don't have the support that
OL,7,Fwe need to help our children, so we
OL,8,Fare having to be creative and look at
OL,9,Fthe ways which we can support them,
OL,10,Fwhile using limited budgets and
OL,11,Fresources."
OL,13,FIn Leeds, waiting times for an
OL,14,Feducation, health and care (EHC) plan
OL,15,F- which can unlock additional funding
OL,16,Ffor the school - can take up to 18
OL,17,Fmonths, well beyond the 20 week
OL,18,Fstatutory target.
