OL,6,FMs Almond also warned that it can take
OL,7,Fmore than five years for an autism or
OL,8,FADHD diagnosis.
OL,10,F"Children are coming in without a
OL,11,Fdiagnosis because of the waiting list
OL,12,Ftime for that and we are just finding
OL,13,Fthat we are just unable to meet the
OL,14,Fneed," she added.
