OL,3,C'Chaotic and broken': The SEND crisis
OL,4,Cfailing scores of children
OL,6,FSir Geoffrey Clifton-Brown, chairman
OL,7,Fof the PAC, has called on the
OL,8,FDepartment for Education to, within
OL,9,Fthe next sixth months, set out the
OL,10,Fprovision which children with Send
OL,11,Fshould expect and what inclusive
OL,12,Feducation looks like.
OL,14,F"This report must serve as a line in
OL,15,Fthe sand for government," he said.
OL,17,F"Every day that goes by, for families
OL,18,Fnot receiving the right support, is
OL,19,Fanother day closer to a lost
OL,20,Fgeneration of young people."
