OL,6,F"We are already making progress by
OL,7,Finvesting #1 billion into Send, #740
OL,8,Fmillion for councils to create more
OL,9,Fspecialist places in mainstream
OL,10,Fschools and through our Curriculum and
OL,11,FAssessment Review which will look at
OL,12,Fbarriers that hold children back from
OL,13,Fthe best life chances."
OL,15,FMeanwhile, Bo is now getting one to
OL,16,Fone support funded by the council,
OL,17,Fwhich is already making a huge
OL,18,Fdifference, but it is a temporary
